Class AbstractMacroSerialPortDevice

java.lang.Object
  de.akuz.osynce.macro.AbstractMacroSerialPortDevice
All Implemented Interfaces:
Macro
Direct Known Subclasses:
MacoRXTXDevice
public abstract class AbstractMacroSerialPortDevice
extends java.lang.Object
implements Macro

Abstract implementation of the Macro interface. This should be the basis for all serial port based implementations. It expects a property called "portname".

Author:
Till Klocke
